rows.label: tlk45320124_02_msg0001
rows.name:
We've managed to avoid war with
Invidia, but that doesn't mean we
can slack off with our training.

rows.label: tlk45320124_02_msg0002
rows.name:
In Temperantia for example, the
Gulan army didn't move, but that
doesn't mean they won't next time.

rows.label: tlk45320124_02_msg0003
rows.name:
Superbians and Gulan have to train
every day in order to protect this city.
Train till we spit blood if needs be...
